@EXPORTS
[filename]/route.ts: GET — stream video file from data/videa/ directory

@FUNCTIONS
GET(request, {params:{filename}}) → Response
  purpose: read video file from disk & stream with proper content-type & range headers
  side-effects: file (read from data/videa/)
  called-by: VideoPlayer component

@STANDARDS
- Supports HTTP Range requests for video seeking
- Content-Type: video/mp4
- Files served from data/videa/ (not public/)

@WARNINGS
- File I/O on every request — no CDN caching
- Filename not sanitized for path traversal — verify security
